name: 03-Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
content:
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

Data Profiling:

  • Distribution of faults by location and severity.
  • Frequency of event types and log features.

Descriptive Analysis:

  • Severity Distribution: % of low, medium, and critical faults.
  • Event-Type Analysis: Most frequent event categories causing high severity.
  • Resource Impact: Severity grouped by resource_type.
  • Location Heatmaps: Identifying critical hotspots.

Visualizations:

  • Histograms of severity distribution.
  • Bar charts of top log features correlated with severity.
  • Location-based severity density maps.
